'''''Once a Year, Every Year'''''  ([[Italian language|Italian]]: ''Tutti gli anni una volta l'anno'')  is a [[List of Italian films of 1994|1994]] [[Cinema of Italy|Italian]] [[comedy film]] written and directed by [[Gianfrancesco Lazotti]].<ref name="90-00 M-Z">{{cite book|author1=Roberto Chiti |author2=Enrico Lancia |author3=Roberto Poppi |title=Dizionario del cinema italiano: I Film|publisher=Gremese Editore, 2002|isbn=8884401372}}</ref><ref name=Mereghetti>{{cite book|last=Paolo Mereghetti|title=Il Mereghetti|publisher=B.C. Dalai Editore, 2010|isbn=8860736269}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=David Rooney|title=Review: ‘Once a Year, Every Year’ |url=https://variety.com/1994/film/reviews/once-a-year-every-year-1200409143/|accessdate=25 April 2014|newspaper=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=October 30, 1994}}</ref>

